data.description:
Welcome to this beautifully updated home nestled in the heart of Vass. This home boasts plenty of room for all guests and loved ones to come visit and stay.

As you step inside, you are greeted by coffered ceilings in the dining room. The open concept helps connect the living/dining/kitchen, perfect for entertaining or family gatherings. The kitchen features upgraded granite countertops, backsplash, and stainless steel appliances.

The home offers 4 bedrooms, including a primary bedroom with an en-suite bathroom featuring a tub and separate shower. The home also features a two-car garage and a laundry room for added convenience.

Outside, the backyard offers a peaceful oasis with a covered patio area, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or relaxing in the evening as the sun sets over the trees

Located just minutes from US-1, this home offers the best of small-town living with easy access to nearby amenities. 

Don't miss the opportunity to claim this as your dream home!
